> Who is a good upholsterer in the greater Los Angeles, Orange County area.
> Want to get my seats done right. Have a camper bed in back, want it to match
> the front seats and do my front door panels and kick panels to match too.

For stock upholstery, you see a good upholsterer in the mirror every
morning.  Just get a pre-sewn upholstery kit, some replacement padding,
and set aside one afternoon per seat.  It isn't difficult at all.

